OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWindy in the
OL,6,Fnorth with outbreaks of rain this
OL,7,Fevening, heavy at times, then turning
OL,8,Fdrier overnight. Cloud reaching
OL,9,Fsouthern areas later, bringing coastal
OL,10,Fand hill fog to the southwest and some
OL,11,Fpatchy rain and drizzle elsewhere.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FCloud and patchy rain
OL,14,Fclearing the far south through the
OL,15,Fday. Largely dry elsewhere with sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Remaining windy in the
OL,17,Fnortheast. Cool in the northwest, warm
OL,18,Fin the southeast.
